data.description:
Spacious one owner home located in the gated community of Indian Harbor. Open concept floorplan with a huge living area featuring surround sound, floating shelves and luxury vinyl plank flooring. Study with French doors off of the foyer is perfect for a home office situation. This versatile floorplan also features a Bonus-media room that could easily be converted to a fifth bedroom. Spacious kitchen features quartz countertops, wrap around breakfast bar, large pantry and lots of cabinet space. Split bedroom arrangement with an ensuite master bedroom. Master bathroom features dual sinks, walk in shower with a seat and a huge master closet. Huge backyard with a double gated wood fence.  HOA community includes pool, clubhouse, boat ramps and playground. Minutes from scenic lake Granbury and 10 minutes from historical Granbury square. 
Show and sell this home.
